Insider Activity


Individual




Richard Neil Haythornthwaite



Mr. Richard N. Haythornthwaite is Non-Executive Chairman at Centrica Plc, Chairman at MasterCard, Inc., Chairman at MasterCard International, Inc., Sloan Fellow at Massachusetts Institute of Technology, President at PSA Energy Holdings SPC, Chairman at Southbank Centre Ltd., Chairman at World Wide Web Foundation, President at PetroSaudi International (Uk) Ltd., and Chairman-Operating Business at PSI (UK) Ltd. He is on the Board of Directors at National Museum of Science & Industry.
Mr. Haythornthwaite was previously employed as Non-Executive Chairman by Network Rail Ltd., Partner by STAR Capital Partners Ltd., Chief Executive Officer & Director by Invensys Plc, Chief Executive Officer by Lafarge Cement UK Ltd., President-Venezuela Division by British Petroleum Co. Plc, General Manager-Magnus Oilfield by BP Exploration, Non-Executive Director by Imperial Chemical Industries Ltd., and President by BP Venezuela Holdings Ltd. He also served on the board at Premier Oil Plc, Cookson Group Plc, and Land Securities Group Plc.



